
=====
Howto
=====

Fetch data and commit to wiki
-----------------------------

Just run:

$ python ccbot.py


Adjust wiki pages
-----------------

Just edit the template pages in template/ directory. Then run:

$ python ccbot.py

to update the wiki pages.


Adjust maps
-----------

Edit the template map XML files in template/ directory. Then run:

$ python view.py test

The map data XML will be generated in the worldmap/ directory. You can preview it in
your browser, for example:

$ cd worldmap
$ firefox world.swf?data_file=worldmap_total.xml

Then update the wiki site if everything is ok:

$ python ccbot.py

